10_2744 kRSNacandraH nAːma kazcit AːsIːt.
10_2745 saH rupavAːn mahAːDanikaH ca .
10_2746 dEːveːna tasmEː sarvaM dattam AːsIːt.
10_2747 sundarIː guNavatIː ca BAːryAː, uttamaH santAːnaH,priyatamAːH bAːnDavAːH,guNavantaH suhRdaH ca tasya Aːsan.
10_2748 taTAːpi tasya pUːrNAː santuSqiH na AːsIːt.
10_2749 mama pAːrzveː sarvam asti .
10_2750 ataH BAːgyavAːn asmi eːva .
