10_2787 teːna kIːdRzaM PalaM prAːptaM iti punaH vaktavyaM na asti Kalu.
10_2788 yasya budDirbalaM tasya
10_2789 moːhana ! AːgacCa putra ! Boːjaneː vilambaH Bavati ! roːhiNIː aBavat .
10_2790 AːgacCAːmi mAːtaH ! idAːnIːM keːzaveːna saha kiYcit sandeːzavinimayaM karoːmi, moːhanaH uttaraM dattavAːn .
10_2791 putra ! keːzavastu ameːrikAːyAːM nivasati .
10_2792 Aːm matah ! idAːnIːm inqaraneːqa- mAːDyameːna AːvayoːH samparkaH asti .
10_2793 samprati sawgaNakeːna sampreːSitaH sandeːzaH kSaNeːnEːva saptasamudrasya pAːraM yAːti .
10_2794 eːtAːdRzam asti AːDunikaM jIːvanam ! asya sawgaNaka-yantrasya AːviSkAːreːNa udyoːgaH, zikSAː, manoːraYjanAːdi sarveːSu kSeːtreːSu vikAːsaH jAːtaH .
10_2795 satyaM dUːraBAːSa-vAːyuyAːnAːdiBiH dUːrasTasya saMsAːraH samIːpam AːyAːti, param iNqaraneːqamAːDyameːna tu aDunAː vasuDAː eːva kuqumbakaM jAːtam .
10_2796 dUːradarzanasya AːviSkAːreːNa aDunAː sarvasAːDAːraNAːH sarvAːn kAːryakramAːn dRzyAːn ca pazyanti .
10_2797 vidyutAː laByateː prakAːzaH vAːyuzca .
10_2798 gEːsa-inDanam, tAːpakaraNam, zIːtakam ityAːdIːni nAːnAːviDAːni vEːjYAːnikoːpakaraNAːni AːDunikaM jIːvanaM saMvarDayanti .
10_2799 ahoː ! vijYAːnasya camatkAːraH sarveːSu kSeːtreːSu dRzyateː .
10_2800 Bavatu himAːlayasya sarvoːccaziKaram aTavAː prazAːntamahAːsAːgarasya gAːmBIːryam, atidUːrasTaH mawgalagrahaH Bavatu aTavAː mAːnavoːdarasTaH sUːkSmakIːqaH -sarvam idAːnIːM draSquM jYAːtuM ca zakyateː .
10_2801 vijYAːnasya eːteːna bahuviDeːna vikAːseːna saMsAːrasya sarveː prAːNinaH lAːBAːnvitAːH Bavanti .
10_2802 paraM vijYAːnasya upayoːgaH loːkakalyAːNAːya eːva kartavyaH, na tu vinAːzAːya .
10_2803 vidyAːyAːH budDiruttamAː.
10_2804 kasmiMzcit sTAːneː catvAːroː brAːhmaNakumAːrAːH parasparaM mitraBAːveːna vasanti sma .
